Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.62,CRKuro,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.18,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Tenhle plán nás zabije.
