Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.31,ScoreboardL,SCORE,0,0,0,,Seirin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.31,ScoreboardR,SCORE,0,0,0,,Kyoritsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.88,CRKuro,RIKO,0,0,0,,Paráda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.36,CRKuro,TSUCHIDA,0,0,0,,Dal smeč!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.26,CRKuro,AUDIENCE 1,0,0,0,,Vážně smečoval?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.32,CRKuro,AUDIENCE 2,0,0,0,,Úžasné! Ten kluk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:39.51,CRKuro,AUDIENCE 3,0,0,0,,To je Kiyoshi! Kiyoshi Teppei, \NŽelezné srdce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.95,CRKuro,PLAYER 4,0,0,0,,{\i1}Železné srdce?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.43,CRKuro,PLAYER 4,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdo nám neřekl, že proti němu budeme hrát!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.30,CRKuro,HYUGA,0,0,0,,Už s tím Železným srdcem běžte někam!
